snippet.title: Funny Media Group
snippet.description:
Welcome to Funny Media Group where all things funny live!

The funniest entertainment in the world.

Funny Media Group is building a platform for the funniest entertainment in the world. Our Los Angeles facility was created for comedy shows with a live audience. We are producing 15- to 30-minute specials, for both up-and-coming and established comedians.
